      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>春节零食促销</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #D32F2F;\n            --accent-color: #FFD54F;\n            --bg-color: #F4F4F5;\n        }\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        body {\n            font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n            background-color: var(--bg-color);\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header, section, main, aside, footer {\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: auto;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 3rem 1.5rem;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n        }\n        .content-section {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            margin-top: 1.5rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n        .content-section h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n        }\n        .content-section p {\n            color: #555;\n        }\n        .aside-section {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-top: 1.5rem;\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0.5rem 0;\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2rem;\n            }\n            .content-section, .aside-section {\n                padding: 1rem;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <section id=\"hero-section\" class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>春节零食盛宴，全场优惠欢享</h1>\n        <p>把节日的喜悦带回家，精选零食低至五折，限时抢购！</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <main id=\"product-showcase\" class=\"content-section\">\n        <h2>热销零食推荐</h2>\n        <p>美味多样，口感纯正，价格实惠，让您挑选满意。</p>\n    </main>\n\n    <section id=\"promotion-info\" class=\"content-section\">\n        <h2>当前优惠活动</h2>\n        <p>全场满100减20，满200减50，活动截止至正月十五。</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <aside id=\"purchase-guide\" class=\"aside-section\">\n        <h2>购买与配送指南</h2>\n        <p>支持支付宝、微信支付，全国快递配送，联系客服热线400-123-4567。</p>\n    </aside>\n\n    <footer id=\"site-footer\">\n        <p>© 2024 欢乐零食有限公司 | 用心为您提供节日美味</p>\n        <p>关注我们的微信与微博，获取最新促销与新品信息</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"
